s at\n$z\\gtrsim3$, we suggest that, as a first approximation, LGRBs can be used as\ndirect tracers of the CSFR in this redshift range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 16:38:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-18"}
