ive to other\nproposals for UDG formation in isolated galaxies, demonstrating that UDGs can\npotentially be formed through multiple mechanisms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 16:42:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2021 03:29:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
