BEC\ntheories. We show how the increase is connected to the structure of the\nparticle-particle vertex. Our results suggest while nematicity may be intrinsic\nproperty of bulk FeSe, is not the primary force driving the superconducting\npairing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 18:24:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2022 12:19:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 23 Apr 2022 14:47:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-26"}
