odes have a perturbative role at the Rayleigh anomaly only on the\nlarger periodic rectangular pattern of miniarrays. Considerable fluorescence\nenhancement of dipolar emitters is achievable at spectral locations promoting\nthe C and U resonances on the composing nano-objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 May 2020 09:02:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-21"}
